Experience the perfect blend of live music and delicious food at Sugarshack Downtown. Join us for a memorable dining experience featuring both inviting indoor seating and charming outdoor options, all while enjoying a vibrant atmosphere that elevates your meal. Don't miss out on a night filled with great tastes and unforgettable tunes!

Sugarshack Downtown is a live music restaurant brought to you by the founders of the popular live music YouTube channel, Sugarshack Sessions.  Set in the beautiful iconic downtown of Bonita Springs FL, Sugarshack Downtown features incredible craft beer, craft pizza, and other mouth-watering cuisine wrapped in an immersive live music setting featuring local, regional, and national music acts. Sugarshack Downtown brings the community together with great food, great drinks, and amazing live music for an experience to be enjoyed by all.
